Title: Night Games
Writer: David Hughes, Mai Zetterling (screenplay), Mai Zetterling (story)
Actors: Ingrid Thulin, Keve Hjelm, Jörgen Lindström, Lena Brundin
Plot: The story about a man who's trying to get rid of his memories from his past. He grew up in an upperclass-family in a castle and now revisits the castle with his fioncee.
